Package com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.importer.release

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DescriptionReleaseFile
    Generates file name matching patterns for description files.
    DescriptionTypeRefSetReleaseFile
    Generates file name matching patterns for description type reference set file.
    LanguageRefsetReleaseFile
    Generates file name matching patterns for language reference sets.
    ReleaseFile
    Abstract superclass for all release files whose location has to be detected when a zip file or a directory is selected for import.
    ReleaseFileSet
    Provides a way to validate if a set of relative paths constitute a valid release directory or archive, and converts symbolic component types into path names.
    ReleaseFileSetSelector
    Provides a method for querying multiple release file set configurations, and return the first one which reports a list of path names to be a valid release root.
    ReleaseFileSetSelectors
    Configures the two release file set selector instances from an externally supplied property file.
    ReleaseIdentifier
    Stores the country-namespace pair (if present) and the release date found in release file name parts.
    SimpleReleaseFile
    Generates file name matching patterns for core terminology files (excluding descriptions).
